headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of O'Reilly (ORLY)
summary: O'Reilly currently trades at $1,425 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 370% since April 2020, tripling the S&P 500’s 122% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 23.4%.
